snippet.title: Atari 2600 Longplay [088] Chuck Norris Superkicks (US)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: RickyC

I never knew a game like this existed. Looks surprisingly nice but I wished it had a proper ending. Each route you take has a chance of being blocked at the end. walking on the grass destroys your time very quickly.

Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
